imdb.plot outline: Hosted by comedians Alex Weber and Zainab Johnson and will surprises hotel guests by turning an elevator into the set of a trivia game show. After they choose a floor, guests-turned-contestants must answer as many questions as they can in order to win cash. The more questions they answer correctly, the higher the elevator moves. But if they get one question wrong, they'll lose it all and head back down to the lobby.
imdb.title: Cash Lift
